MODIFICATIONS
-------------
This is a MODIFIED version of the Original Work. Changes relative to the
upstream "magento/inventory" project include, but are not limited to:

  * Curated community bug fixes and performance improvements applied ahead
    of their acceptance (if any) into the upstream project.
  * Repackaging the 73 distributed modules under the "jeanmarcos/inventory"
    Composer package, which replaces the individual "magento/module-inventory-*"
    packages for Magento 2.4.8.
  * Removal of the proprietary "InventoryRequisitionList" module, which is
